  "text": "X-ray data collection, structure solution and refinement X-ray diffraction data were collected at 100 K: from GCG GCGGC on BL 14.2 beam line at the BESSY synchrotron (Berlin) to the resolution of 2.05 Å ; from GC(8-BrG)GCG GCGGC and GC(8-BrG)GCGGC on EMBL X11, DESY, Hamburg, to the resolution of 1.45 Å and 0.97 Å , respectively. The crystals were cryoprotected by 20% glycerol (v/v) in the mother liquor. The data were integrated and scaled using the program suite DENZO/ SCALEPACK [CITATION_1] .",
